fe With Secure NFC , With multi-function NFC, WP8 Pro supports Google Pay, on-vehicle payment and so on. You can quickly and securely shop in stores, apps and online 5000mAh Large Battery ,using safer, longer life lithium battery, longer standby time, safer and more durable GPS & GLONASS , with precise positioning sensors, can help you locate your position no matter where you are, even in remote places Fingerprint recognition and face unlocking ,Side fingerprint unlocking design, just touch to unlock. When the screen is turned on, you can quickly detect multiple feature dimensions of the face, and perform high-precision intelligent matching, and complete the unlocking process in an instant Custom keys , you can quickly access your personal favorite content through three different scenarios such as single-click, double-click, and long-press. These can be set through the custom keys in the menu Global 2G, 3G and 4G frequency bands: As long as the region supports 2G, 3G and 4G, you can carry OUKITEL WP8 Pro with you. Multi-function toolbox: The application toolbox has compass, noise test, level, magnifying glass, protractor, plumb bob, alarm bell, etc., which can meet your needs in different scenarios SIM card: 2 SIM card slots:Type 1: Nano SIM * 1 + Nano SIM * 1;Type 2: Nano SIM * 1 + TF / SD card * 1 Smooth operation: keep the game video from freezing when fighting enemies 360° protection: The convex design at the four corners and the corresponding frame can also prevent damage. 6.49 Inch IPS HD+ Immensce Display The 6.49 inch incell huge high-definition screen with a 90% screen-to-body ratio provides a larger field of vision while maintaining the comfortable grip of the mobile phone. With in-cell full-fit screen technology, the color performance is more accurate, and the picture is transparent and clear. It can bring good display effects whether it is a game or a movie picture. 4GB RAM + 64GB ROM & MT6762D Octa-Core OUKITEL WP8 Pro rugged smartphone has an MT6762D eight-core processor with 4GB of running memory, so that WP8 PRO outdoor smaartphone has a faster running speed and smooth application experience. 64GB of body memory, and support additional 256GB of memory expansion via SD card to accommodate all the content you want, run more APP storage memory, Facebook, photos, videos, games, music, install your favorite apps in In the mobile phone, bid farewell to the trouble of insufficient memory, the long-term experience is smoother and more intimate, and it can run multiple APPs at the same time without lag WP8 PRO 360°waterproof！ OUKITEL WP8 Pro rugged smartphone has IP68 dustproof and waterproof performance. It can be easily handled by immersing it in 1.5m water depth for 2 hours and has excellent waterproof function. You can use your mobile phone with peace of mind even in rainy days. Even if your mobile phone is accidentally drenched with water, it will not be damaged. It is an extra protection for your life 360° Dust-proof！ OUKITEL WP8 Pro mobile phone has 99% professional dustproof performance, provides you with a full range of body protection, suitable for users in all walks of life, and is an ideal companion for outdoor sports enthusiasts. 1.5M Drop Resistance！ OUKITEL WP8 Pro 4g phone has a solid body and alloy frame structure. The front is covered with scratch and drop resistant Corning Gorilla Glass 3. When falling from a height of 1.5M, it can still be intact, allowing you to feel the sturdy side of WP8 Pro. The three-proof anti-compression and anti-fall structure greatly improves the performance and effectively protects the body. High temperature resistance The main body of OUKITEL WP8 Pro rugged smartphone has passed the high and low temperature endurance test. The WP8 Pro made of high and low temperature resistant material can adapt to most extreme areas, so that it does not shut down at low temperatures, and does not become hot at high temperatures, making it easier to use outdoors. It can be used normally within the working temperature range of -40°c-70°c. (function(f) {f(window.P._namespace("AplusModule"));}(function(P) {
