    } Armor 9 Specifications: OS: Latest Android 10 Display: 6.3-inch FHD+ Waterdrop Screen (Resolution: 1080*2340) CPU Processor: Helio P90 (MT6779) + CPU Core: Octa-core 64-bit 2.2GHz Storage: 8GB RAM + 128GB ROM, TF/SD Card up to: 2TB Cameras: Rear Camera: Samsung 64MP +2MP +2MP + Front Camera: 8MP Flash: Four Rear flash Integrated FLIR Thermal Imaging: Support Battery: 6600mAh (Built in) with 18W fast charging Navigation: GPS+GLONASS+BEIDOU+Galileo Audio Jack: 3.5mm CTIA Features: OTG, NFC, Face ID, Recognition, Bluetooth V2.1+EDR, V3.0+HS, V4.2+HS, V5.0 Other: VoLTE, Blinking Notification/Battery Status Light, WiFi 802.11 a/ac/b/g/n (2.4G+5G), Hotspot & tethering, E-compass, HiFi, Real-time heart rate detection Integrated FLIR Thermal ImagingFLIR Lepton with MSX technology Measurable Temperature Range: -10℃ - 400℃5MP Auxiliary Imaging CameraVisualizes heat that is invisible to the naked eye, highlighting temperature contrasts.Pre-install MyFLIR2 App Application Scenarios Surveillance: See in total darkness, in parking structures, in alleys. Search & Rescue: Help find missing persons, see through smoke and light brush. Pest Control: Detect areas of potential entrance points for rodents, find bee and hornet nests Outdoor Adventure: Safety determine if your campfire is out, find and track animals, find members of your party through fo- liage and in total darkness, check surroundings. Home and Auto: Identify insulation problems, water leaks, window issues, plumbing problems, potential electrical connection issues, automotive issues such as misalignment, brake wear, heating and cooling systems, heated seat problems. Pipes & Ducts: Identify blockages in ventilation systems and pipe work, measure temperature of furnace and water pipes Professional Use: Building repair, mechanics, electricians, home inspectors, construction industries all can view, create, and share reports right from their smartphone without the need for a computer. Waterproof 3 in 1 Endoscope Supported: A Versatile Industrial Inspection Camera Ulefone Armor 9 features an expansion interface for flexible endoscope on the left. The endoscope is waterproof and comes with semi-rigid cable, you can use the endoscope into many hard-to-reach, narrow anc confined places at home or outdoors, such as HVAC, vent pipe, car engines, air conditioners, sofa corners, bathtube pipes, toilets, etc... [ Note: the endoscope is not included. ] Samsung 64MP Rear Camera The super camera system of Armor 9 features Samsung GW1 64MP ultra-high resolution image sensor with Te-tracell and integrated 3D HDR technoloqy, let you capture more detailed images and video even in mixed and challenging lighting environment. Four high brightness flash on the back helps to capture the treasure and beauty of the world even under circumstance of insufficient light. 64MP Ultra High-Resolution Primary Camera SAMSUNG ISOCELL Bright GW1 ƒ/1.89 large aperture, 6 piece lens supports 4-in-1 Super Pixel (16MP, 1.6μm) ISOCELL Plus Technology Support Super-PD ultra-fast focusing 2MP Depth Sensor Photo resolution: up to 9280x6944 pixels Video resolution: up to 1920x1080 pixels Quad-LED Flash Rear camera photography features: Night photography, HDR Mode, Pro mode, high-resolution photos, Beautify Mode, Panorama mode, AI scene detection, Gif, TimeLapse, Intelligent Scanning, Face Cute, Bokeh 8MP selfie camera: ƒ/2.2 large aperture, 5 piece lens Front camera photography features: Beautify mode, Panorama mode, Gif, Filter, Watermark, TimeLapse, HDR Incredible AI Performance | Android 10 OS Latest and Powerful MediaTek Helio P90 Processor Helio P90 which comes with 4.6 times higher performance than Helio P60 & P70. There is almost no lag when loading up apps and switching between most apps. The Newest Android 10 System With Dark Theme Some of the newest ways to control your privacy, customize your phone and get things done. It’s Android, just the way you want it. Support Dark Theme, Sound Amplifier, Gesture Navigation, Privacy Controls, Location Controls, Security Updates, Family Link, etc. 8GB + 128GB Runs without Limits for a Full-Speed Experience Armor 9 packs with large 8GB RAM and 128GB of internal storage, which will provide the phone much buffer space and faster running performance, definitely meet your every need for storage space. 2G/3G/4G Global Frequency Bands: Ulefone Armor 9 becomes a true global phone, which means you can use 90% areas over the world. Armor 9 adds an extra 4G band-Band 66, that means the network support for North America making it even more appealing. Check compatibility with your local bands before purchase! 2G: GSM: B2/3/5/8 | CDMA 1X: BC0/BC1 3G: WCDMA: B1/2/4/5/8 | TDSCDMA: B34/B39 | CDMA EVDO: BC0/BC1 4G: LTE-FDD: B1/2/3/4/5/7/8/12/13/17/18/19/20/25/26/28A/28B/66 | LTE-TDD: B34/38/39/40/41 NOTE: If the Armor9's network can't work please set the APN first or let us know to help you solve it. IP68&IP69 &MIL-STD-810G The Ulefone Armor 9 meets a whole list of advanced performance standards, including IP68, IP69K. MIL-STD-810G. It is tough enough to withstand sudden drop, and are resistant to submersion up to a maximum depth of 1.5m underwater for up to 30 minutes. It is also drop tested onto concrete from up to 1.2 meters to prove its rugqed credentials and ensure there is no damage to the phone's performance. Defines Superb Durability. Armor 9 is built by soft TPU and aluminium alloy reinforced polycarbonate material with superb craftsmanship, which can provide effective buffer protection for the phone while accidentally falling down. Besides, the four reinforced corners will also prevent drop- ping damage effectively. 360 all-round protection provides Armor 9 unrivalled durability and ruggedness. The advanced sealing technology and solid structure make the Armor 9 more than simply a little splash-proof. Waterproof stoppers are specially designed for the USB port, earphone jack, and SIM card slot, effectively prevent water entering into the phone. Components that are exposed to the outside also have a high-density macro-molecule coating for waterproofness. Certification: CE, FCC, TAC IMEI, MSDS, UN38.3, IEC62133, IP68, IP69K, MIL-STD-810G Manual 1*Charging indicator card Please ensure that all caps on the phone are securely sealed before underwater activities. Dry the phone afterwards before charging, otherwise the phone will be damaged by water and possibly dead. Packing List : 1*Armor 9 rugged phone 1* US Charger plug (9V/2A) 1*Type C USB Cable 1*OTG Cable 1*Type C to Micro USB Adapter 1*Tempered Glass Screen Protector 1*Sling 1*SIM Needle 1*Multiple Languages Manual 1*Charging indicator card

