 large aperture, 5 piece lens Front camera photography features: Beautify mode, Panorama mode, Gif, Filter, Watermark, TimeLapse, HDR Incredible AI Performance | Android 10 OS Latest and Powerful MediaTek Helio P90 Processor Helio P90 which comes with 4.6 times higher performance than Helio P60 & P70. There is almost no lag when loading up apps and switching between most apps. The Newest Android 10 System With Dark Theme Some of the newest ways to control your privacy, customize your phone and get things done. It’s Android, just the way you want it. Support Dark Theme, Sound Amplifier, Gesture Navigation, Privacy Controls, Location Controls, Security Updates, Family Link, etc. 8GB + 128GB Runs without Limits for a Full-Speed Experience Armor 9 packs with large 8GB RAM and 128GB of internal storage, which will provide the phone much buffer space and faster running performance, definitely meet your every need for storage space. 2G/3G/4G Global Frequency Bands: Ulefone Armor 9 becomes a true global phone, which means you can use 90% areas over the world. Armor 9 adds an extra 4G band-Band 66, that means the network support for North America making it even more appealing. Check compatibility with your local bands before purchase! 2G: GSM: B2/3/5/8 | CDMA 1X: BC0/BC1 3G: WCDMA: B1/2/4/5/8 | TDSCDMA: B34/B39 | CDMA EVDO: BC0/BC1 4G: LTE-FDD: B1/2/3/4/5/7/8/12/13/17/18/19/20/25/26/28A/28B/66 | LTE-TDD: B34/38/39/40/41 NOTE: If the Armor9's network can't work please set the APN first or let us know to help you solve it. IP68&IP69 &MIL-STD-810G Please ensure that all caps on the phone are securely sealed before underwater activities. Dry the phone afterwards before charging, otherwise the phone will be damaged by water and possibly dead. Packing List : 1*Armor 9 rugged phone 1*Endoscope 1* US Charger plug (9V/2A) 1*Type C USB Cable 1*OTG Cable 1*Type C to Micro USB Adapter 1*Tempered Glass Screen Protector 1*Sling 1*SIM Needle 1*Multiple Languages Manual 1*Charging indicator